Subject: [PATCH 3/3] Add KVM VM status in user session info

Test:

If KVM is not open

https://x.x.x/kvm/kvmActiveStatus

{
"kvmActiveStatus": 0
}

IF KVM is open

https://x.x.x/kvm/kvmActiveStatus

{
"kvmActiveStatus": 1
}

